column5: Picked up this guy out wandering about on the Big Lake     Travelling on the Bike was very good  Should be a Great weekend out there!!  Rick
Sweet Laker  Thanks for the conditions report... Screw work. Im going fishing..
Yes Dawg  Yesterdays Slush has all tightened up  Even the water around the cracks was froze.  Walkers, Sleds and Bike all staying on top of the crusty snow.  Rick
Nice fish bud. I,ll be out Sunday.
